<HEADLINE> Dow Loses 19; Nasdaq Drops 40  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK (AP) -- The Dow Jones industrial average is down 19
points in today's early going. Losing issues on the New York Stock
Exchange hold a 6-5 lead over gainers.
</P>
<P>
   The Nasdaq Composite Index is off 40 points and the Standard &AMP;
Poor's 500 Stock Index is down six points.
</P>
